Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.80,0:00:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.63,0:00:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.34,0:00:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.25,0:00:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.92,0:00:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.97,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.98,0:01:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.18,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.58,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.23,0:01:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐,請看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此廣大的庭院,美麗的新居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是為了妳\N我不計付出一切代價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?妳滿不滿足?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿足,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,我不能這麼輕易就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來今天會是個好天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.64,0:03:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#26 五代愕然!響子醋罈大爆發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,對不起喔\N突然把妳叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我跟我老公\N相約碰面的時間延後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.67,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,我也很想見妳\N所以就跑來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳跟高中時代一樣\N一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看我這樣\N有一陣子我很消沈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,我有聽說,音無老師過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少有個孩子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.62,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是帶個孩子再婚的話\N應該很麻煩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有考慮再婚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.03,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是妳總不能一輩子一個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是無所謂,妳還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像妳這麼漂亮\N至少有兩三個男人在追求妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛,也不是沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我總是無法忘掉過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.06,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的個性就是這樣\N或許這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過還是早點做打算比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管妳怎麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.27,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間一久的話\N總會忘記死去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.74,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是其他的男人不見得\N能等到那個時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.18,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像在跟一位房客太太\N還有我爸媽說話似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也這麼說妳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.79,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,一天到晚叫我再婚\N聽得我耳朵都長繭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳啊,哪天他們不說了\N妳就完蛋了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦率一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都說同樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再婚啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論兩年還是三年\N我都會等妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.83,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.51,0:06:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果對象是五代的話\N再婚得等上個四五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.32,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他能夠愛我這麼久嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是早點跟他約定\N等他大學畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.93,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到時候我幾歲了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生小孩還是30歲前比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.90,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這點來說,如果是三鷹\N現在馬上就能辦到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭,我在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,沒什麼好著急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩人都說了願意等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真稀奇,五代居然會打掃房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他的女朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說要來這裡玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.21,0:07:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還說要來煮飯給他吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來還說要幫他洗衣服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是五代居然說不好意思\N耍酷婉拒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.16,0:08:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種沒出息的男人\N居然也有女人願意服侍他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代也太不像話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事竟然拿來炫耀\N到處去跟人家講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他什麼都沒說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是聽到他們講電話的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛!五代那個人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾脆就讓女朋友\N直接幫他煮飯洗衣服嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,這樣大概可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,這樣大概可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.26,0:09:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?今天是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,是的,我有空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.17,0:10:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興喔\N你還特地到外面來等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.14,0:10:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說\N我想做奶油燉牛肉給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以帶了高麗菜,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,不要叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.75,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小聲一點,悄悄進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦,我的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個好登對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好,我是七尾小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.58,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.15,0:11:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸,太大聲了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要跟管理員亂說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.47,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?\N你做了見不得人的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是什麼見不得人的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.31,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不是不明白你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別看管理員那樣\N其實她是個大醋罈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,有時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會吃醋啊,太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就叫她幫你做飯洗衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是故意說那麼大聲給我聽的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛這樣氣呼呼的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩個人的交往\N看起來還很清純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰氣呼呼的了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.68,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代想幹嘛,關我什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.49,0:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼會擦起指甲油?\N有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我今天要跟三鷹約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳跟三鷹教練有進展了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.77,0:12:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為妳以前沒說過約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.18,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還說只是兩人見個面\N不是什麼約會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天居然還擦了指甲油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前是那麼說的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是第一次來男生的房間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點髒亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這裡的牆壁顏色不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡最近才整修過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前一直有個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼聲音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.72,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,給我開門\N我知道你在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次再把牆壁弄壞的話\N我不會再忍氣吞聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了沒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲音不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是有老鼠啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.81,0:13:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不是那種可愛的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好親熱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.33,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的…這是情勢所逼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你的房間,隨你高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.28,0:14:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家很害怕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不太好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家會怕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.86,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我會很困擾的\N真的不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在親熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,我說你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.18,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修那片牆得花不少錢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道妳會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳今天好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我要去跟三鷹約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.46,0:15:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是要去約會啊,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這樣啊,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天他沒有開車來接妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的車子現在送去車檢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我又不是跟車子約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江,你們也要出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.99,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來想做奶油燉牛肉給他吃\N可是失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以想請他到我家來吃飯\N向他賠罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有跟她說不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是叫人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得是這一帶沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,竟然選在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那麼在車站前的\N“珍愛”見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在愛犬美容院的二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然選在愛犬美容院…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠子,惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來,不可以這樣,惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,褲子弄得髒兮兮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,請進來裡面一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了,真的不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代簡直像小津江養的小白臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.98,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,三鷹比他可靠多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小…小姐妳聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.20,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,三鷹比五代自愛多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只因為人長得帥\N就容易被人誤會花心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹比較…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,因為我很怕狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,如果你不嫌棄我的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瑪,別鬧了,快點走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.57,0:19:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她怎麼不去換獎品呢\N小鋼珠都掉滿地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,小鋼珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.47,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好厲害喔\N我還是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣勢真是驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還送我東西帶回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我簡直就像個小白臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣厚臉皮交往下去\N真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳的罐頭掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.69,0:21:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要了,送給你吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很重的樣子\N我來幫妳拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了\N我不想接受男人的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.16,0:21:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是不是和三鷹吵架了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這麼問?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,只是覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們約會玩得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.37,0:22:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的約會還真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.47,0:22:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然抱了這麼多罐頭回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不重嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.71,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不太舒服的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很冷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我高興怎麼樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.19,0:22:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都跟你無關吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了!\N這球飛得很遠,真的很遠!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.46,0:22:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中外野手拼命地退後接球\N接得到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.47,0:22:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,飛出去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.24,0:22:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全壘打!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.71,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地點應該是這裡沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.14,0:22:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要放我鴿子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不記得我有做什麼\N讓她生氣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.21,0:23:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎竟然被烤肉串給拐走了\N真是條大笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家擔心得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.65,0:23:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠到底跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.31,0:23:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.01,0:24:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「惣一郎不見了?\N回憶是烤肉串的香味」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黃昏時刻回首看到你的身影時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.69,0:24:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內心湧起了一股\N忘卻已久的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.24,0:24:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.22,0:24:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.13,0:24:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.23,0:24:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.37,0:25:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.21,0:25:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕

